This is the landing page for an app called 'thinkr' that helps e-commerce businesses by suggesting improvements to their store and automating processes. thinkr primarily helps Shopify stores by installing from the Shopify app store in order to read and write data to Shopify. thinkr can also connect to other applications like Facebook Ads, Klaviyo, and other related apps. thinkr has a very specific design language that is featured on this site and tries to make more difficult processes easier to fulfill our mission of enabling e-commerce stores to scale much more efficiently with the help of AI.